thread.title: WM

author: WM
title: WM
text:
I'm pretty particular about my food so I was pleasantly surprised by the quality and flavor of food provided by munchery. I ordered an entree with salmon, turkey chili, side of bread, and kid's pasta and the flavor and quality of all were pretty good. Definitely better than the average diner or takeout.
Portion size was on the larger side. Packaging was eco friendly. Nutrition info was included on all packaging.
